  <front>
    <title>LSP Attribute in ERO</title>
    <seriesInfo name="Internet-Draft" value="draft-margaria-ccamp-lsp-attribute-ero-00"/>
    <author initials="C." surname="Margaria" fullname="Cyril Margaria"/>
    <author initials="D." surname="Schroetter" fullname="Dirk Schroetter"/>
    <author initials="G." surname="Martinelli" fullname="Giovanni Martinelli"/>
    <date day="18" month="April" year="2012"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>LSP attributes can be specified or recorded for whole path, but they
   cannot be specified as part of an Explicit Route Object (ERO).  This
   document extend the semantic for RSVP ERO object with a new subobject
   to carry LSP attributes.</t>
    </abstract>
  </front>
</reference>